OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784146710
OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,FMore than 90% of parents in Northern
OL,8,FIreland believe the summer holidays
OL,9,Fbring both financial and emotional
OL,10,Fpressure for their families.
OL,12,FAccording to new research, 40% of
OL,13,Fparents say this pressure leads to
OL,14,Fstress on family life, with over half
OL,15,F(56%) worrying their children will
OL,16,Fspend too much time on screens.
OL,18,FMore than a third (35%) of parents
OL,19,Ffeel anxious about the summer and its
OL,20,Ffinancial implications.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
