OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784146710
OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,FThe statistics were commissioned by
OL,8,Fthe charity Save the Children UK as
OL,9,Fpart of its No Summer Break from
OL,10,FPoverty campaign to highlight the
OL,11,Freality of families' experiences this
OL,12,Fsummer.
OL,14,FIt found 40% of local parents struggle
OL,15,Fto afford trips/days out for their
OL,16,Fchildren, 40% are stressed about the
OL,17,Fpressures of summer, and 29% are
OL,18,Fworried about increased bills over the
OL,19,Fholiday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
