CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784146710
OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,FIt also found a quarter of families
OL,8,F(26%) save all year just to be able to
OL,9,Fafford summer.
OL,11,FSave The Children NI said it is
OL,12,Fworking directly with families through
OL,13,Fpartners in the region, where child
OL,14,Fpoverty rates are at 22% (100,000
OL,15,Fchildren), to ensure childhoods are
OL,16,Fnot missed out on due to poverty.
OL,18,FLaura Feeney from the charity said
OL,19,Fmany families are already in crisis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
