OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,F"We know summer is a real strain for
OL,8,Fmany of the families we and our
OL,9,Fcommunity partners support through our
OL,10,Ffamily grants," she said.
OL,12,F"These families are already in crisis,
OL,13,Fand the mental toll poverty brings
OL,14,Fthem can get heavier at this time of
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,F"We want to see real awareness,
OL,18,Fempathy and action from our political
OL,19,Fleaders.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@OO]tD@AOUyD@AOU
