OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,F"No matter what time of year, child
OL,8,Fpoverty should be their top priority."
OL,10,FJoanne Dougan from STEP Dungannon said
OL,11,Fmany struggle without free school
OL,12,Fmeals.
OL,14,F"When schools break up for summer,
OL,15,Ffamilies struggle as free school meals
OL,16,Fcome to an end," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@fO]vD@AOUxD@PO]
