CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784146710
OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,F"It's not just those who qualify for
OL,8,Fsupport, many families fall just above
OL,9,Fthe eligibility threshold, missing out
OL,10,Fon free school meals and uniform
OL,11,Fgrants despite facing real financial
OL,12,Fpressure.
OL,14,F"With the high cost of childcare and
OL,15,Fextra household expenses during the
OL,16,Fholidays, many are left asking, where
OL,17,Fis the additional money supposed to
OL,18,Fcome from?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@KO]
