OL,3,CMore than 90% of parents feel
OL,4,Cfinancial pressure every summer,
OL,5,Cresearch finds
OL,7,FLouise McCullough, a mother from
OL,8,Fparents support group Elevate East,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Summer automatically brings
OL,10,Fthat extra financial and mental
OL,11,Fstress. I know I feel the strain of it
OL,12,Ffor months in advance.
OL,14,F"As a parent you do your best to give
OL,15,Fyour kids the summer experiences and
OL,16,Fmemories they deserve, but it's so
OL,17,Fmuch pressure on my shoulders."
